          <p class="form-subtitle">Fill out the form below and we'll get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
          <ContactForm />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- What to Expect -->
  <section class="what-to-expect">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-title">
        <h2>What to Expect</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="expect-grid">
        <div class="expect-item">
          <div class="expect-icon">‚ö°</div>
          <h4>Quick Response</h4>
          <p>We aim to respond to all inquiries within 24 hours during business days</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="expect-item">
          <div class="expect-icon">üí¨</div>
          <h4>Personalized Consultation</h4>
          <p>We'll discuss your specific needs and provide tailored solutions</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="expect-item">
          <div class="expect-icon">üìã</div>
          <h4>Detailed Proposals</h4>
          <p>Receive comprehensive quotes and project plans for your review</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="expect-item">
          <div class="expect-icon">ü§ù</div>
          <h4>Transparent Communication</h4>
          <p>Clear, honest communication throughout our entire collaboration</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Services Overview -->
  <section class="services-overview">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-title">
        <h2>How We Can Help</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="help-grid">
        <div class="help-card">
          <h4>üé¨ Film Production</h4>
          <p>Need a documentary, NGO video, or commercial content? We deliver professional quality with social impact.</p>
          <a href="/services#production" class="link-arrow">Learn more ‚Üí</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="help-card">
          <h4>üåç Film Fixing</h4>
          <p>Filming in Rwanda? We handle all logistics, permits, crew, and equipment for international productions.</p>
          <a href="/services#fixing" class="link-arrow">Learn more ‚Üí</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="help-card">
          <h4>üé® Animation Services</h4>
          <p>Professional animation production for educational, commercial, or storytelling purposes.</p>
          <a href="/animation" class="link-arrow">Learn more ‚Üí</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="help-card">
          <h4>üéì Training Programs</h4>
          <p>Want to learn filmmaking or animation? Join our professional training programs.</p>
          <a href="/training" class="link-arrow">Learn more ‚Üí</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="faq">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-title">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-grid">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h4>How much do your services cost?</h4>
          <p>Pricing varies depending on project scope, duration, and requirements. Contact us for a detailed quote tailored to your specific needs. We offer competitive rates while maintaining professional quality.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h4>How long does production typically take?</h4>
          <p>Timeline depends on project complexity. A simple NGO video might take 2-3 weeks, while a documentary could take several months. We'll provide a detailed timeline during consultation.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h4>Do you work with international crews?</h4>
          <p>Yes! We regularly provide fixing services for international productions filming in Rwanda, including permits, logistics, local crew, and equipment.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h4>How can I apply for training programs?</h4>
          <p>Contact us through this form expressing your interest. We'll provide information about upcoming cohorts, application requirements, and available scholarships.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h4>Are training programs free?</h4>
          <p>We offer both free and subsidized training. Priority for free programs goes to youth and women from underserved communities. All profits from commercial work fund these programs.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h4>What equipment do you have available?</h4>
          <p>We have professional cinema cameras, lighting kits, audio equipment, drones, and complete post-production facilities. Full equipment list available upon request.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Map Placeholder -->
  <section class="location-map">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-title">
        <h2>Find Us in Kigali</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="map-placeholder">
        <div class="map-content">
          <h3>MEB CBC Rwanda</h3>
          <p>Kigali, Rwanda</p>
          <p class="map-note">üìç Contact us for specific location details and directions</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="final-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-box">
        <h2>Ready to Start Your Project?</h2>
        <p>Whether it's a production, training inquiry, or partnership opportunity, we're here to help make it happen.</p>
        <div class="cta-contact">
          <a href="tel:+250795512502" class="btn btn-primary">üìû Call Us Now</a>
          <a href="mailto:mebrmp2022@gmail.com" class="btn btn-secondary">‚úâÔ∏è Send Email</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .contact-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: #f8f9fa;
  }
  
  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
    gap: 4rem;
  }
  
  .contact-info h2 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .contact-info > p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  
  .info-items {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .info-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  
  .info-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  
  .info-content h4 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  
  .info-content p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  
  .business-hours {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }
  
  .business-hours h4 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .business-hours p {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }
  
  .social-links {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 15px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }
  
  .social-links h4 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .social-icons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  
  .social-icon {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .social-icon:hover {
    background: var(--accent);
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }
  
  .form-container h3 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .form-subtitle {
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .what-to-expect {
    background: white;
  }
  
  .expect-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  
  .expect-item {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 15px;
  }
  
  .expect-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .expect-item h4 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .expect-item p {
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  .services-overview {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    color: white;
  }
  
  .services-overview .section-title h2 {
    color: white;
  }
  
  .help-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  
  .help-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }
  
  .help-card h4 {
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }
  
  .help-card p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .link-arrow {
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .link-arrow:hover {
    transform: translateX(5px);
  }
  
  .faq {
    background: #f8f9fa;
  }
  
  .faq-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  
  .faq-item {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 15px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }
  
  .faq-item h4 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .faq-item p {
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  .location-map {
    background: white;
  }
  
  .map-placeholder {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 4rem;
    text-align: center;
    border: 2px dashed #ddd;
  }
  
  .map-content h3 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .map-content p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin: 0.3rem 0;
  }
  
  .map-note {
    margin-top: 1.5rem !important;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  .final-cta {
    background: var(--primary);
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .cta-box h2 {
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .cta-box p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  
  .cta-contact {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .contact-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
    
    .cta-contact {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .cta-contact .btn {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 300px;
    }
  }
</style>